segments.text: This is a special meeting of the Seattle City Council.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: Will the clerk please call the roll?
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: The purpose of this special meeting is to hold an executive session regarding pending potential or actual litigation.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: If there's no objection, the agenda will be adopted.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: Not seeing or hearing any objection, the agenda is indeed adopted.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: We will now move into executive session and I will share this information so we're officially there.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: As presiding officer, I'm announcing that Seattle City Council will now convene an executive session.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: The purpose of the executive session is to discuss pending potential or actual litigation.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: The council's executive session is an opportunity for the council to discuss confidential legal matters with city attorneys as authorized by law.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: A legal monitor from the city attorney's office is always present to ensure the council reserves questions of policy for open session.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: I expect the time of the executive session to end at 1.30.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: The Executive Session is to be extended beyond that time.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: I will announce the extension and expect the duration.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: At the conclusion of this Executive Session, the City Council meeting will be adjourned.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: The next regularly scheduled City Council meeting is today at 2.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00

segments.text: So with that, we'll move into Executive Session.
segments.speaker: SPEAKER_00
